# Data databases are formatted by FracturedJSON (j-brooke.fracturedjsonvsc) on save in
# VS Code — its aligned-colon style is intentional. Prettier must never touch these.
*.jsonc
*.json

# Markdown (docs / specs / AGENTS / CLAUDE / README) is hand-authored with manually aligned
# tables — the primary working surface here. Prettier reflows tables + prose and fights that
# layout, so it must not touch markdown. Format these by hand.
*.md

